title: Kurt Vile - three songs recorded live at The Current
description:
Kurt Vile visited The Current studio, where he played this solo, acoustic versions of songs from his new album, "Watch My Moves," as well as a selection from his 2011 album, "Smoke Ring From My Halo." 

Songs Played
0:00 Mount Airy Hill (Well Gone)
05:11 Like Exploding Stones
09:45 Peeping Tomboy
